====Verb====
{{en-verb|abrad|ing}}

# {{transitive}} To [[rub off|rub]] or [[wear off]]; to [[waste]] or [[wear away]] by [[friction]]; to [[damage]] or make [[rough]]; as, to abrade rocks.

